data.description: At home in the country.  This spacious home offers an open concept floorplan;  family room w fireplace, spacious kitchen w dining bar, plenty of counter space & cabinets plus an adjoining covered porch for additional outside living space.  1st floor owner suite w walk-in closet, dual vanities, soaking tub & separate shower.   Upstairs is a cozy lounge area, 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  Outside you will love the detached  double garage/workshop, pool and 10 acres of land.  There is a boat ramp close by for fishing & water sports days.
